title: Google parent Alphabet pops 9 on earnings beat
text:
Google parent Alphabet pops 9% on earnings beat 
CNBC Friday 23rd October, 2015 
Google parent Alphabet beats earnings estimates 
Google parent, Alphabet, topped expectations on top and bottom lines, sending shares higher in after-hours trading, reports CNBC's Josh Lipton.
